### Creatomate API转发 - 获取renders列表
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/proxy/creatomate/v2/renders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY

### Creatomate API转发 - 创建render
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/proxy/creatomate/v2/renders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template_id": "your-template-id",
  "modifications": {
    "Text": "Hello World"
  }
}

### Creatomate API转发 - 获取模板列表
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/proxy/creatomate/v1/templates
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY

### 通用API转发示例（动态API名称）
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/proxy/creatomate/v2/renders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY

